'''拉斐爾·納達爾'''<br />
納達爾今年一開始打進[[2010年卡塔尔埃克森美孚公开赛|卡塔尔埃克森美孚公开赛]]決賽，以0-6, 7-6<sup>8</sup>, 6-4敗給俄羅斯著名球員[[尼古萊·達維登科|尼古萊·達維登科]]。<ref name="自动生成1">{{Cite web |work=Fox Sports |title=Davydenko beats Nadal to win Qatar title |url=http://msn.foxsports.com/tennis/story/nikolay-davydenko-beats-rafael-nadal-to-win-qatar-open-010910 |date=2010-01-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418004113/http://msn.foxsports.com/tennis/story/nikolay-davydenko-beats-rafael-nadal-to-win-qatar-open-010910 |archivedate=2010-04-18 |accessdate=2010-11-16 }}</ref>[[2010年澳洲網球公開賽|澳洲公開賽]]，他在八強敗給[[安迪·穆雷|安迪·穆雷]]。納達爾在紅土賽季[[2010年蒙地卡羅大師賽|蒙地卡羅大師賽]]，決賽以6-0, 6-1直落二盤擊敗[[費爾南多·貝爾達斯科|費爾南多·貝爾達斯科]]取得勝利，創下在此地連續六年奪冠，寫下公開賽以來ATP單一賽事最長連霸紀錄，也一掃去年羅馬大師賽以來，長達11個月一冠未得的低潮。<ref>{{Cite web |work=Guardian |title=Rafael Nadal thrashes Fernando Verdasco to win Monte Carlo Masters |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2010/apr/18/rafaelnadal-tennis |date=2010-04-18 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2012-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511115251/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2010/apr/18/rafaelnadal-tennis |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他奪得[[2010年羅馬大師賽|羅馬大師賽]]冠軍，決賽以7-5, 6-2直落二盤擊敗同胞[[大衛·費雷爾|大衛·費雷爾]]這是他在此項賽事的第五座冠軍。<ref>{{Cite web |work=Signon San Diego |title=Nadal defeats Ferrer to win 5th Rome Masters|url=http://www.signonsandiego.com/news/2010/may/02/nadal-defeats-ferrer-to-win-5th-rome-masters/ |date=2010-05-02}}</ref> 納達爾也在家鄉的[[2010年馬德里大師賽|馬德里大師賽]]奪得冠軍，決賽重演去年對陣的戲碼，結果以6-4, 7-6<sup>5</sup>直落二盤復仇[[羅傑·費德勒|羅傑·費德勒]]<ref>{{Cite web |work=Canada.com |title=Record-breaking Nadal beats Federer to win Madrid Masters |url=http://www.canada.com/sports/Nadal+beats+Federer+Madrid+Masters/3035473/story.html?id=3035473 |date=2010-05-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109125048/http://www2.canada.com/sports/nadal+beats+federer+madrid+masters/3035473/story.html?id=3035473 |archivedate=2012-11-09 |accessdate=2010-11-16 }}</ref>，拿下第18座大師系列賽冠軍，超越[[安德烈·阿加西|安德烈·阿加西]]成為大師系列賽最多奪冠紀錄保持人，納達爾這次健康又狀態調整極佳，結果又和前年一樣以不失一盤重奪[[2010年法國網球公開賽|法國公開賽]]冠軍，以6-4, 6-2, 6-4直落三盤擊敗[[羅賓·索德靈|羅賓·索德靈]]，從後者奪回屬於自己的榮耀<ref>{{Cite web |work=huffingtonpost |title=Rafael Nadal Wins 2010 French Open, Beats Robin Soderling In Straight Sets To Win Title |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/06/06/rafael-nadal-wins-french_n_602148.html |date=2010-06-06 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222902/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2010/06/06/rafael-nadal-wins-french_n_602148.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 這場法國公開賽決賽的勝利，不僅拿下法網第五座冠軍與第七座大滿貫單打錦標，也使積分再度超越費德勤重登世界第一。完成前所未有的紅土大滿貫 (同年連奪三項紅土大師賽與法網)，並以22連勝完美結束今年的紅土賽季。之後草地賽季的[[2010年女王盃|女王盃]]，納達爾在八強被同胞[[費利西亞諾·洛佩斯|費利西亞諾·洛佩斯]]以7-6<sup>5</sup>, 6-4直落二盤淘汰終止24連勝。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/8735543.stm |title=Rafael Nadal suffers shock Queen's Club loss to Lopez |work=BBC |date=2010-07-13 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820123419/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/8735543.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>納達爾在[[2010年溫布頓網球錦標賽|溫布頓錦標賽]]第二度舉起了金盃，決賽以6-3, 7-5, 6-4直落三盤擊敗[[托馬什·貝爾迪赫|托馬什·貝爾迪赫]]，將大滿貫錦標數量累計到八座。<ref>{{Cite web |work=Fox Sports |title=Nadal tops Berdych for eighth Slam title |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/sports/tennis/wimbledon10/news/story?id=5353895 |date=2010-07-06 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2016-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127112709/http://sports.espn.go.com/sports/tennis/wimbledon10/news/story?id=5353895 |dead-url=no }}</ref>納達爾首次[[2010年美國網球公開賽|美國公開賽]]封王，雖然決賽一度因雨延遲仍以6-4, 5-7, 6-4, 6-2擊敗[[諾瓦克·喬科維奇|諾瓦克·喬科維奇]]，以24歲之姿完成[[網球大滿貫#職業金滿貫|職業金滿貫]]和鎖定年終世界第一<ref>{{cite news |url=http://blog.gvtnews.com/2010/09/13/rafael-nadal-completes-career-golden-slam-wiht-us-open-win.aspx?ref=rss |title=Rafael Nadal Completes Career Golden Slam with US Open Win and Joins "Magnificent Seven" |work=Global Village Tennis News |date=2010-09-13 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111165749/http://blog.gvtnews.com/2010/09/13/rafael-nadal-completes-career-golden-slam-wiht-us-open-win.aspx?ref=rss |archive-date=2020-01-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> <ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2010/09/Other/Nadal-ATP-World-Tour-Champion.aspx |title=Nadal Clinches Year-End No. 1 For Second Time |work=ATP World Tour |date=2010-09-13 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2015-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130193026/http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2010/09/Other/Nadal-ATP-World-Tour-Champion.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> 亞洲硬地賽季，納達爾[[2010年日本網球公開賽|日本公開賽]]首次參賽，決賽以6-1, 7-5直落二盤擊敗法國球員[[加埃爾·蒙菲爾斯|加埃爾·蒙菲爾斯]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.demotix.com/news/470195/nadal-wins-2010-rakuten-japan-open-tennis-championship-tokyo |title=Nadal Wins 2010 Rakuten Japan Open Tennis Championship in Tokyo |work=demotix |date=2010-10-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721175002/http://www.demotix.com/news/470195/nadal-wins-2010-rakuten-japan-open-tennis-championship-tokyo |archivedate=2011-07-21 |accessdate=2010-11-16 }}</ref>。[[2010年巴黎大師賽|巴黎大師賽]]，納達爾因練球過度，而肩膀受傷<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newsdaily.com/stories/tre6a44ys-us-tennis-paris-nadal/ |title=Nadal misses Paris Masters with shoulder injury |work=News Daily |date=2010-10-10 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

