'''羅傑·費德勒'''<br />

費德勒在年初的第一項大滿貫，[[2010年澳洲網球公開賽|澳洲公開賽]]，決賽以6-3, 6-4, 7-6<sup>11</sup>直落三盤擊敗[[安迪·穆雷|安迪·穆雷]]，奪得第四座澳網冠軍與第16座大滿貫單打錦標<ref>{{Cite web |work=NY Times |title=With Australian Title, Federer Returns From Vulnerable to Invincible |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/01/sports/tennis/01tennis.html?_r=1 |date=2010-01-31 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926033009/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/01/sports/tennis/01tennis.html?_r=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，費德勒之後並沒有進入任何一場巡迴賽決賽，直到法國公開賽的前哨站[[2010年馬德里大師賽|馬德里大師賽]]才進入決賽，結果被宿敵[[拉斐爾·納達爾|拉斐爾·納達爾]]以6-4, 7-6<sup>5</sup>直落二盤擊敗<ref>{{Cite web |work=NY Times |title=Renewing Rivalry, Nadal Tops Federer in Madrid |url=http://straightsets.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/05/16/renewing-rivalry-nadal-tops-federer-in-madrid/ |date=2010-05-16 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109110813/https://straightsets.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/05/16/renewing-rivalry-nadal-tops-federer-in-madrid/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[2010年法國網球公開賽|法國公開賽]]在八強以6-3, 3-6, 5-7, 4-6敗給[[羅賓·索德靈|羅賓·索德靈]]宣告衛冕失敗。法國公開賽期間，費德勒完成ATP700勝與紅土150勝<ref>{{Cite web |work=ATP World Tour |title=Roland Garros Friday Federer Wins 700th Match |url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2010/05/Roland-Garros/Roland-Garros-Friday-Federer-Wins-700th-Match.aspx |date=2010-05-28 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2010-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601060936/http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2010/05/Roland-Garros/Roland-Garros-Friday-Federer-Wins-700th-Match.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>他之後在兩項ATP巡迴賽進入決賽屈居亞軍，[[2010年哈雷網球公開賽賽|哈雷網球公開賽]]，被前世界第一[[萊頓·休伊特|萊頓·休伊特]]以3-6, 7-6<sup>4</sup>, 6-4，中止對後者15連勝<ref>{{Cite web |work=Tennis X |title=Hewitt Overcomes Federer Spell, Wins Halle Title |url=http://www.tennis-x.com/xblog/2010-06-13/4412.php |date=2010-06-13 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820120344/http://www.tennis-x.com/xblog/2010-06-13/4412.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2010年溫布頓網球錦標賽|溫布頓錦標賽]]在八強以4-6, 6-3, 1-6, 4-6敗給[[托馬什·貝爾迪赫|托馬什·貝爾迪赫]]也宣告衛冕失敗 費德勒在溫布頓第一輪完成大滿貫200勝<ref>{{Cite web |work=rediff Sports |title=Federer joins an elite club |url=http://sports.rediff.com/slide-show/2010/jun/22/slide-show-1-roger-federer-joins-elite-club.htm |date=2010-06-21 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2019-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421215817/http://sports.rediff.com/slide-show/2010/jun/22/slide-show-1-roger-federer-joins-elite-club.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；北美夏季硬地賽季的[[2010年羅傑斯盃|羅傑斯盃]]，被尋求衛冕的[[安迪·穆雷|安迪·穆雷]]以7-5, 7-5直落二盤擊敗。<ref>{{Cite web|work=Mail Online|title=Awesome Andy retains Rogers Cup after straight-sets win over Federer in Toronto|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/tennis/article-1303382/Andy-Murray-beats-Roger-Federer-retain-Rogers-Cup-Toronto.html|date=2010-08-15|accessdate=2010-11-16|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220428/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/tennis/article-1303382/Andy-Murray-beats-Roger-Federer-retain-Rogers-Cup-Toronto.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 費德勒在[[2010年辛辛那提大師賽|辛辛那提大師賽]]衛冕成功，決賽以6<sup>5</sup>-7, 7-6<sup>1</sup>, 6-4苦戰三盤逆轉擊敗美國球員[[马尔迪·菲什|马尔迪·菲什]]<ref>{{Cite web |work=Fox News |title=Roger Federer wins Cincinnati Masters title, tying Bjorn Borg for 5th in career titles |url=http://www.foxnews.com/sports/2010/08/22/federer-beats-fish-cincinnati-masters-championship-tieing-borg-th-career-titles/ |date=2010-08-22 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2010-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101117202840/http://www.foxnews.com/sports/2010/08/22/federer-beats-fish-cincinnati-masters-championship-tieing-borg-th-career-titles/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。費德勒在[[2010年美國網球公開賽|美國公開賽]]進入四強，以7-5, 1-6, 7-5, 2-6, 5-7大戰五盤敗給塞爾維亞天王[[諾瓦克·喬科維奇|諾瓦克·喬科維奇]]，他也在[[2010年上海大師賽|上海大師賽]]進入決賽，以3-6, 2-6直落二盤敗給[[安迪·穆雷|安迪·穆雷]]<ref>{{Cite web |work=Latest Sports Buzz |title=Shanghai ATP Masters 1000: Roger Federer Loses to andy murray in Shanghai Final |url=http://www.latestsportsbuzz.com/?p=8141 |date=2010-10-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227054659/http://www.latestsportsbuzz.com/?p=8141 |archivedate=2010-12-27 |accessdate=2010-11-16 }}</ref>。費德勒在[[2010年斯德哥爾摩公開賽|斯德哥爾摩公開賽]]拿到今年第三座冠軍，決賽以6-4, 6-3直落二盤擊敗德國球員[[佛羅里恩·梅爾|佛羅里恩·梅爾]]<ref>{{Cite web |work=Guardian |title=Roger Federer wins Stockholm Open to equal Pete Sampras mark |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2010/oct/24/roger-federer-stockholm-open-pete-sampras |date=2010-10-24 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2010-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101027194555/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2010/oct/24/roger-federer-stockholm-open-pete-sampras |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他所奪得的生涯第64座冠軍與美國天王[[皮特·桑普拉斯|皮特·桑普拉斯]]的生涯冠軍數量相等。費德勒在家鄉[[2010年大衛杜夫瑞士室內賽|大衛杜夫瑞士室內賽]]決賽，以6-4, 3-6, 6-1激戰三盤擊敗[[諾瓦克·喬科維奇|諾瓦克·喬科維奇]]，奪得生涯第65座冠軍超越皮特·桑普拉斯，他的生涯冠軍數量排行第四位<ref>{{Cite web |work=The Sports Review |title=Federer wins Basel title back from rival Djokovic |url=http://www.thesportreview.com/tsr/2010/11/roger-federer-basel-novak-djokovic/ |date=2010-11-07 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2010-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101110012017/http://www.thesportreview.com/tsr/2010/11/roger-federer-basel-novak-djokovic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。費德勒在[[瑞典|瑞典]][[斯德哥爾摩|斯德哥爾摩]]達成職業生涯第900場並奪下那場勝利<ref>{{Cite web |work=ATP World Tour |title=Federer Wins In 900th Tour-Level Match; Soderling Close To Finals Qualification |url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2010/10/42/Stockholm-Thursday-Blake-Into-QFs.aspx |date=2010-10-21 |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archive-date=2010-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024184507/http://www.atpworldtour.com/News/Tennis/2010/10/42/Stockholm-Thursday-Blake-Into-QFs.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

